OL,4,Coverspend, O'Dowd tells MLAs
OL,6,FStormont is on course for an overspend
OL,7,Fof #387 million in the current
OL,8,Ffinancial year, Finance Minister John
OL,9,FO'Dowd has told MLAs.
OL,11,FMr O'Dowd told the Finance Committee
OL,12,Fthat the Department of Education alone
OL,13,Fhas a projected overspend of #247
OL,14,Fmillion as he urged ministers to make
OL,15,Fdecisions so they could live within
OL,16,Ftheir budgets.
