OL,4,Coverspend, O'Dowd tells MLAs
OL,6,FHe told the committee: "I have asked
OL,7,Fall ministers to endeavour to find
OL,8,Ffurther efficiencies to help fund the
OL,9,Fpressures facing departments."
OL,11,FThe minister added: "It is likely that
OL,12,Fwe are looking at a position where we
OL,13,Fwill be in an overspend despite my
OL,14,Frepeated advice to departments of the
OL,15,Fneed to live within their allocated
OL,16,Fbudgets, and of the consequences of
OL,17,Fany overspend.
