OL,4,Coverspend, O'Dowd tells MLAs
OL,6,F"Executive colleagues have a lot of
OL,7,Fwork to do, their accounting officers
OL,8,Fhave a lot of work to do to drive
OL,9,Fefficiencies forward."
OL,11,FThe minister said the "main drivers"
OL,12,Fof the overspend were the health and
OL,13,Feducation departments.
OL,15,FHe said health was forecast to
OL,16,Foverspend by #139.4 million and
OL,17,Feducation by #247 million.
OL,19,FMr O'Dowd said a "significant chunk"
OL,20,Fof the overspends related to pay
OL,21,Fawards.
